                    <h2>SOLUTION</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <p>
                            Fake IDs are usually copies of genuine IDs or illegally modified genuine IDs made by
                            unauthorised persons.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            There is currently no way of quickly verifying if the ID you are looking at is a true and
                            correct document. We’ve seen many times in cinematic movies that it’s easy to create a
                            fake ID and if you run a search on Google you’d be surprised how many businesses
                            actually promote this type of service.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <p>
                            VeriDoc Global has developed a solution that involves embedding a QR code on an ID with a
                            unique digital hash inside the QR code. The hash holds a string of information that is
                            then placed on the blockchain network for security, verification and most important end
                            user validation.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Using any QR code reading app, scan the QR code on the ID card and the app will show you
                            the true document produced by the issuer. This allows you to compare and see if the ID
                            card is an original or a fake.
                        </p>
                    </div>
